Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.30,0:00:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字叫江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.80,0:00:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本是高中生工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被灌下毒藥而身體變小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體雖然變小 頭腦還是一樣的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.20,0:00:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有迷宮的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓大家久等了的前後篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔他們的同學會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去的情份就算被破壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.30,0:00:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相永遠只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.61,0:00:21.09,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}hyakunen buri no seikimatsu
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.70,0:00:27.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}nake to iwarete boku ha waratta
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.86,0:00:39.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}hisakata buri no seikimatsu
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.04,0:00:45.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}hiroi sekai he tobidashite yuku
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.00,0:00:52.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}kodomo no koro ni wakarikaketeta
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.18,0:00:58.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}koto ga otona ni natte wakara nai mama
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.69,0:01:01.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}eraku mo nai shi
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.69,0:01:04.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}rippa demo nai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.69,0:01:10.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}wakatteru no ha mune no dokidoki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.00,0:01:16.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}kotae demo nai hontou demo nai
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.00,0:01:22.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}shinjiteru no ha mune no dokidoki
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.08,0:01:28.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(310,30)}mune no dokidoki dake
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.00,0:01:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小五郎同學會殺人事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.10,0:01:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你的同學會不帶我們去 有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.60,0:01:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳幹嘛去那裡 那可是我的同學會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你五年前就帶我一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.30,0:01:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是事務所不能夠沒人看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.10,0:01:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是剛好有大案子怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是真的有案子 爸爸你出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.70,0:01:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也不能受理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.60,0:02:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也很想去洗溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不對 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.50,0:02:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.60,0:02:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以請你們吃頓好吃的補償你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.50,0:02:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們才不要什麼好吃的 你就帶我們去溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.70,0:02:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.80,0:02:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近一陣子國內旅行要比國外旅行要貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子 我要付三個人的費用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為我想過沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這才是主因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.30,0:02:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人搶銀行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.60,0:02:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往哪兒逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.90,0:02:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等 你們兩個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我站住 看你往哪兒跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.10,0:02:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.70,0:02:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別過來 我要開槍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.10,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你抓到了銀行的搶匪了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這對我名偵探毛利小五郎來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就像是甕中捉鼈一樣容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.90,0:03:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼 你剛才踢磚頭怎麼會那麼有勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我怕那個壞人會對叔叔開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.40,0:03:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一緊張就踢了那塊磚頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.65,0:03:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到剛好踢中了他的槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼說 是柯南救了我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.90,0:03:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.60,0:03:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼來說的話 爸爸為了表示謝意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.20,0:03:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶你的救命恩人一起去洗溫泉才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.20,0:03:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於我 就以柯南監護人的身份一起跟去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這根本是兩回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.00,0:03:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.70,0:03:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳又在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我的公司就在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是出來吃飯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳就是崛越阿姨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是小蘭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.20,0:03:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一次妳也會來溫泉的同學會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然我一定會去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰說妳可以去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們那天再見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.60,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.50,0:04:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蘭她是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這孩子真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這一次又建了一個大功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勞你幫忙 太感謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點小事沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.00,0:04:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.70,0:04:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀行搶匪拿的那把槍不需要收回嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請這邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.70,0:04:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.90,0:04:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得那個搶匪的手槍確實是掉在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.80,0:04:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會是這條路上的行人趁著剛才的一陣亂撿走了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得儘快通知局裡去找才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.80,0:04:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過離開一下而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.90,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰拿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然還是出來旅行吃的火車便當好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.20,0:05:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我的同學會一定要帶小鬼來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你五年以前還不是帶我一起去的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候因為妳還小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我總不能丟下妳 自己去參加吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一次要不是柯南救了爸爸你一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸你還不是不能去參加同學會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算沒有這個小鬼出手幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一樣可以輕而易舉地抓到那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.00,0:05:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那支不見的手槍找到了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.10,0:05:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警方也沒有發佈任何的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.80,0:05:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛 警方雖然有做嚴密的搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻還沒有發現它被用來犯罪的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以現在完全沒有線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.00,0:05:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都把那支手槍稱作斯威森M439
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實那個銀行搶匪對槍並不瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他雖然出高價買了一把槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻不知道那把槍到底是真槍還是玩具槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是真的是玩具槍就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.80,0:06:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明注意到那把槍的槍口沒有塞填充物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那把槍受到撞擊都沒有損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可能是真槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.70,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好幾年沒見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從五年前在這裡開同學會就沒有再見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.20,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們米花大學柔道社的同一期畢業生還真難得碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.40,0:06:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一段辛苦練習的日子還真叫人懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.40,0:06:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還好意思說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本都很少來練習的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.72,0:07:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以前總是說天才是不需要練習的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.34,0:07:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以成天到晚都不來練習 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.50,0:07:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以到最後和友校對抗的時候沒有贏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.33,0:07:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就只有你一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那一次比賽是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.40,0:07:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你說的大學時代打遍全校無敵手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是騙人的 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.90,0:07:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們雖然前幾天已經見過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳真的是長大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好 還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳剛才都到哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.30,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露天浴池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露天浴池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡可是男女混浴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旁邊根本就沒有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你們兩個剛才一塊兒去洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.60,0:07:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南他好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我費了好大工夫才帶他去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過剛才真的好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還幫他刷背了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.00,0:07:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流鼻血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是剛才的水太熱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.00,0:08:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是看到小蘭的身體太興奮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.70,0:08:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南他還只是個小孩子 小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.40,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是事蹟敗露的話我就死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個小朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個寄住在毛利家裡的小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還真是可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔阿姨好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.70,0:08:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是米花大學柔道社的主將 綾城行雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多指教 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.20,0:08:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是柔道社第一戰將 大村淳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家說的得分王就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.80,0:08:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是柔道社的美女經理 崛越由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一樣是經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時也是柔道社的偶像 以前叫做木元紀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過現在我是他的老婆了 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.40,0:08:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是社團裡的主將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是柔道社的精神支柱 中道和志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在在千葉縣當警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.00,0:08:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然我是不會像他做警察做到一半就不做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.00,0:08:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.40,0:09:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來大家都是柔道社的主將或偶像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.60,0:09:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都熟悉的名偵探…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會是我們大學時代的照片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.20,0:09:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想讓大家回憶一下所以隨便帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.30,0:09:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們有沒有在聽我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.90,0:09:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以讓我看看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.80,0:09:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這張是我們在京都大會得到優勝的時候拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.60,0:09:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都好年輕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候 中道跟由美好像就已經在交往了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.00,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候還有兩個人傷心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.80,0:09:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿淳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.10,0:09:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美那時候可是柔道社的瑪丹娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在可是我的老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你們兩個現在還在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就跟他斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.30,0:10:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.90,0:10:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連和志都已經有結婚的對象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.40,0:10:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要結婚了嗎 中道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.60,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.20,0:10:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來是打算在正式一點的場合告訴你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想應該今年就會了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼對方是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.40,0:10:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我上司的千金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是在半年前相親時認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一次 我介紹給你們認識認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在再來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當年的瑪丹娜已經是老小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在經濟又這麼不景氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼看著我就要被公司的人事整頓開除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想想 我還真的是不想活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.80,0:10:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說說而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是開玩笑的 幹嘛這麼認真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不要這樣嚇人好不好 由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這樣一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.20,0:10:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是單身的就只剩下我跟阿淳兩個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾脆我們結婚好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑的 玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼還當真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這張照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得不是五年前來這裡照的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.20,0:11:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.00,0:11:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡面還有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.10,0:11:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.70,0:11:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們在桌球場照的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才會放到裡面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.10,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.10,0:11:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待會兒我們一起去打桌球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.90,0:11:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.60,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.40,0:11:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傍晚的時候 我們不是說好了要去看煙火嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.60,0:11:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙火要從六點半才開始放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.70,0:11:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們還有三個多小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要在六點前結束就來得及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.10,0:11:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我突然覺得有點累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到房裡休息去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她還是老樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事都以自己為準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不管別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想由美只是不想和大家一樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.40,0:11:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去打桌球吧 桌球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然 洗溫泉要打打桌球那才像話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.30,0:11:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經好久沒有試試身手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是堂堂的體育老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然也不能遜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.10,0:12:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一局又是我贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就要輪到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點結束 回來打球啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中道叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.65,0:12:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是曾經得過全國大會的個人優勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.00,0:12:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是大學三年級的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.20,0:12:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就那一次而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.90,0:12:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中道叔叔果然是柔道社裡最強的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.10,0:12:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一個人比我的段數還要高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來卻沒有贏過一次比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有這樣的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蘭妳也認識這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.10,0:12:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他今天也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.00,0:12:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的這個人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.90,0:12:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.90,0:12:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然打變化球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.05,0:12:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼那麼快就回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.10,0:12:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.35,0:13:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.15,0:13:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來紀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.75,0:13:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.65,0:13:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個老夫老妻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要這樣玩到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間好像已經不夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.45,0:13:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.15,0:13:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經過六點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.55,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們如果不快點的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.75,0:13:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙火晚會一定擠滿人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們就快點走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我先把球拍跟網子拿回去還了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們先去占位子好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘記叫由美阿姨起床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.85,0:13:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙火就要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會有人叫她起床的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.35,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是每個人都忘記怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.05,0:13:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是回去叫她好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.85,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.15,0:13:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要管她不就好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.75,0:14:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快叫她起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.85,0:14:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,201號 就是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.85,0:14:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.25,0:14:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煙火已經開始放了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.25,0:14:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要開門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為是誰呢 原來是小蘭跟柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.85,0:14:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中道叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不是先過去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是回來叫由美阿姨起床的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看妳還是別叫的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.45,0:14:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最討厭的就是被別人叫起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中道叔叔你怎麼還在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.05,0:14:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打桌球流了一身汗就先去洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.85,0:14:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後就聽到你們的腳步聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.75,0:14:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還正覺得奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.65,0:14:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這家旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我們幾個住宿而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個怎麼也還在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.65,0:15:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼也還在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.75,0:15:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是先去洗澡把一身汗洗掉對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.45,0:15:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我和你們不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在大浴堂洗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.65,0:15:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.85,0:15:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳沒有把由美叫醒可是正確的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.45,0:15:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為她最討厭被人家吵醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是如果沒有把她叫起來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她也一樣會生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.05,0:15:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.95,0:15:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人真的好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南 你可別把手放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蘭 在這裡 這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.65,0:15:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼只有你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.45,0:15:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才我們明明走在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是被人群給擠散的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到那邊去找找看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.90,0:15:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿淳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這趟旅行還真是忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.05,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.05,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟阿淳好不容易找到一個好位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後誰也沒有到那兒去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.95,0:16:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.75,0:16:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿淳 你也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說是要去找他們就一去不回了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.15,0:16:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.95,0:16:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我實在搞不清楚方向了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 忘了這個 喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就只知道自顧自的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美阿姨還沒起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼一說我倒想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美睡了這麼久也應該起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想那傢伙又在鬧彆扭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.45,0:16:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定在怪我們沒把她叫起來看煙火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.05,0:16:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.95,0:16:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼全是一個樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.75,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們大家一起去把柔道社的瑪丹娜叫起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.85,0:16:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說去就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這任性的女人看見大家叫她應該怕了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂 在她面前可別說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.95,0:16:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.65,0:16:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.05,0:16:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.25,0:16:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 妳還在睡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.95,0:16:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我開燈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.75,0:17:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.95,0:17:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.05,0:17:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了我這個警察跟毛利這個偵探之外誰也不可以進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.05,0:17:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.65,0:17:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去叫警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.05,0:17:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.25,0:17:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.45,0:17:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太陽穴上有槍痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.55,0:17:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右手上又拿著槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.25,0:17:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.35,0:17:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一把槍難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個銀行搶匪用的那把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.35,0:17:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.35,0:17:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這把槍的確是斯威森M439
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.05,0:17:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槍身的上面似乎也有撞到東西的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.15,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 由美當天也在現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美? 妳又在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我的公司就在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是出來吃飯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美是一開始就打算這麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才會把這把槍撿走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.65,0:18:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她早就計畫好在同學會上自殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.25,0:18:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.45,0:18:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在下結論還太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們等警方來了以後再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.15,0:18:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.55,0:18:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.45,0:18:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳為什麼非要尋死不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警方還要兩個小時才能到這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說因為今天這一帶都在舉行慶典 到處都很塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.45,0:18:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們怎麼能等兩個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.05,0:18:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來只好由我們來鑑定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.95,0:18:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有誰帶照相機來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛好帶了相機來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那借用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就到房間去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.55,0:19:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒想到今天我們兩個竟然會為由美驗屍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.15,0:19:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的腳趾已經開始僵硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說她已經死了有一段時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我再驗一下屍斑好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.45,0:19:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是她出血這麼多 觀察屍斑也不太可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美身上竟然沒有穿內衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.75,0:19:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.55,0:19:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪的可不只是這一點而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.35,0:19:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美阿姨身上穿的這件浴衣好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.65,0:19:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在大廳時穿的是比較小的一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.45,0:19:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她握著手槍的手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.35,0:19:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在板機外面就已經僵硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一點奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.35,0:19:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是她頭上的…
